text: == Events == * Mael Morda starts a rebellion against Brian Boru in Ireland, which would eventually end in 1014 at the Battle of Clontarf. * Sulayman is restored as Umayyad caliph of Cordoba, succeeding Hisham II. * Benedict VIII becomes pope. Gregory is antipope. * Archbishop Alphege of Canterbury is murdered by his Danish captors. * King Aethelred of England pays Danegeld. * Oldrich succeeds Jaromir as duke of Bohemia. Category:1012
